<p>When topic lock is set, only channel operators can change the topic.</p>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_terminal}>Usage</.help_h4>
<pre>/mode +t    — Enable topic lock
/mode -t    — Disable topic lock</pre>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_link}>See Also</.help_h4>
<p><.help_link topic="cmd-topic">/topic Command</.help_link></p>
